attributes.description: The "TYCHON Endpoint Browser" dashboard provides host visualization data for a single endpoint at a time. The dashboard is a set of several individual views broken down by tabs near the top of the screen. The TYCHON Endpoint Browser â€“ Services and Ports view displays all Services found on hosts, as well as listening ports and ARP Tables.

params.markdown:
### Services and Ports
TYCHON reports what ports are open at the time of the check. It records what process and command was used to open the port and correlates that process if it was started as a service.

attributes.title: [TYCHON] Endpoint Browser - Services and Ports
